---

## 🧠 One-Line Description
Nyaya is an AI fairness SDK and cloud platform that detects and removes hidden caste and religion bias from machine learning models used in India.

---

## ⚠️ The Problem

Modern AI systems used in:
- Hiring platforms  
- NBFC loan approvals  
- Hospital triage systems  

are trained on embedding models like IndicBERT, E5, and mBERT.

These models encode social bias geometrically.

Example:
- Names like Sharma are closer to “intelligent”
- Names like Paswan are closer to “unskilled”

Even if developers never write biased rules, the model still behaves unfairly.

### 📊 Evidence
- IndiBias (NAACL 2024) → Indian language models show caste bias  
- DeCaste (2025) → Bias persists across datasets  
- Nature (Jan 2026) → Structural bias in multilingual embeddings  

---

## ❌ Why Existing Tools Fail

Current fairness tools:
- Require explicit protected labels (not available in India)
- Do NOT support caste proxies like surnames
- Cannot detect embedding-level bias

Result: Bias remains invisible.

---

## ✅ Our Solution — Nyaya

Nyaya solves this using research-backed methods:

### 1. SEAT (Bias Detection)
Measures bias using sentence templates and similarity.

### 2. Hard Debiasing
Removes bias direction mathematically using PCA projection.

### 3. Retroactive Audit
Re-evaluates past decisions to detect unfair outcomes.

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

| Component        | Technology |
|-----------------|-----------|
| Backend API     | FastAPI + Cloud Run |
| Frontend        | Flutter |
| Storage         | Firebase Storage |
| Database        | Firestore + BigQuery |
| Trigger System  | Cloud Functions |
| AI Explanation  | Gemini 1.5 Flash |

---

## 🔌 API Endpoints

### POST /audit
Upload dataset and get bias metrics

Example response:
{
  "dataset_rows": 200,
  "caste_seat_before": 0.72,
  "caste_seat_after": 0.12,
  "demographic_parity_before": 0.61,
  "demographic_parity_after": 0.88,
  "passes_fairness": true
}

---

### POST /retroactive
Re-evaluate past decisions

---

### GET /health
Check if API is running

---

## 📊 Real-World Use Cases

- Hiring platforms → fair resume screening  
- NBFCs → fair loan approvals  
- Healthcare → unbiased patient prioritization  

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

### Backend
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/nyaya-audit  
cd nyaya-backend  
python -m venv env  
source env/bin/activate  
pip install -r requirements.txt  
python main.py  

---

### Frontend
cd nyaya_frontend  
flutter pub get  
flutter run  

